      <title><![CDATA[zabbix-install]]></title>
      <url>/2017/05/15/zabbix-install/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>本文将简要介绍<code>Centos6</code>使用<code>yum</code>安装<code>zabbix</code>的教程<br>硬件、软件以及php扩展要求，部分转自<a href="https://www.abcdocker.com/abcdocker/2181" target="_blank" rel="external"><code>ZABBIX 3.2 基础安装</code></a></p>
<h2 id="硬件配置参考："><a href="#硬件配置参考：" class="headerlink" title="硬件配置参考："></a>硬件配置参考：</h2><p><img src="http://static.zybuluo.com/abcdocker/3beanert2f2hfpyd5a91uca9/image_1b9nessv5ll8qguap91nmf1a9v64.png" alt="硬件配置" title="硬件配置参考实例"></p>
<h2 id="软件配置参考"><a href="#软件配置参考" class="headerlink" title="软件配置参考:"></a>软件配置参考:</h2><p><img src="http://static.zybuluo.com/abcdocker/kp2oetoseghvxfasx886v574/image_1b9nf2duq1lrk16l81pf3ik4mvm6h.png" alt="软件配置" title="软件配置参考实例"></p>
<h2 id="前端配置参考"><a href="#前端配置参考" class="headerlink" title="前端配置参考:"></a>前端配置参考:</h2><p><img src="http://static.zybuluo.com/abcdocker/1gsu04doz0jezwrtwn29be4t/image_1b9nf4bv7a8818e2qec78tmc6u.png" alt="前端配置" title="前端配置参考实例"></p>
<h2 id="安装相关软件"><a href="#安装相关软件" class="headerlink" title="安装相关软件"></a>安装相关软件</h2><ul>
<li>httpd以及扩展需要的库<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ yum install libxml2 libxml2-devel libvpx libvpx-devel httpd-devel libXpm-devel \</div><div class="line">libxmp-devel httpd libjpeg-devel curl curl-devel gettext gettext-devel zlib \</div><div class="line">zlib-devel openssl openssl-devel libzip bzip2-devel gd gd-devel libssh2 libssh2-devel \</div><div class="line">gd gd-devel</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="安装mysql"><a href="#安装mysql" class="headerlink" title="安装mysql"></a>安装mysql</h2><ul>
<li><p>根据Centos安装mysql官方yum源</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ rpm -ivh http://dev.mysql.com/get/mysql-community-release-el6-5.noarch.rpm</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>安装mysql</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ yum install mysql-community-server mysql-community-common mysql-community-client mysql-community-devel</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="安装php"><a href="#安装php" class="headerlink" title="安装php"></a>安装php</h2><ul>
<li>编译安装php以及相关扩展<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ ./configure --prefix=/usr --sysconfdir=/etc --libdir=/usr/lib64  --with-libdir=lib64 \ </div><div class="line">--with-config-file-path=/etc --with-config-file-scan-dir=/etc/php.d \ </div><div class="line">--with-apxs2=/usr/sbin/apxs  --with-pic --with-curl --enable-gd-native-ttf \ </div><div class="line">--with-gettext  --with-openssl --with-pcre-regex --with-zlib  --with-layout=GNU \ </div><div class="line">--enable-exif  --enable-calendar --with-sqlite3 --with-libxml-dir --with-gd --enable-pdo \ </div><div class="line">--enable-xmlreader --enable-xmlwriter --enable-mbstring --enable-json --enable-bcmath \ </div><div class="line">--enable-mbstring --enable-sockets --with-bz2 --with-curl --enable-ftp --enable-sockets \ </div><div class="line">--with-jpeg-dir= --with-png-dir= --with-freetype-dir= --enable-gd-native-ttf \ </div><div class="line">--with-iconv-dir= --with-pdo-mysql=mysqlnd --with-mysqli=mysqlnd \</div><div class="line">--with-mysql=mysqlnd --enable-ssh2</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="安装zabbix"><a href="#安装zabbix" class="headerlink" title="安装zabbix"></a>安装zabbix</h2><ul>
<li><p>安装zabbix官方yum源</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ rpm -ivh http://repo.zabbix.com/zabbix/3.0/rhel/6/x86_64/zabbix-release-3.0-1.el6.noarch.rpm</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>安装数据库文件以及前端文件</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ yum install zabbix-server-mysql zabbix-web-mysql</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>安装zabbix相关程序</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ yum install zabbix-server zabbix-get zabbix-agent</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="创建并导入数据库文件"><a href="#创建并导入数据库文件" class="headerlink" title="创建并导入数据库文件"></a>创建并导入数据库文件</h2><ul>
<li><p>创建zabbix数据库,mysql5.7默认需要设置更为复杂的秘密</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ mysql -uroot -p&lt;your root password&gt;</div><div class="line">mysql&gt; create database zabbix character <span class="built_in">set</span> utf8 collate utf8_bin;<span class="comment">##最好设置utf-8,防止中文乱码</span></div><div class="line">mysql&gt; grant all privileges on zabbix.* to zabbix@localhost identified by <span class="string">'zabbix'</span>;</div><div class="line">mysql&gt; quit;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>导入数据库文件,记住<code>zabbix-server-mysql-3.0.X</code>,是对应自己安装<code>zabbix</code>的版本</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ zcat /usr/share/doc/zabbix-server-mysql-3.0.X/create.sql.gz | mysql -uzabbix -p zabbix</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="设置虚拟主机"><a href="#设置虚拟主机" class="headerlink" title="设置虚拟主机"></a>设置虚拟主机</h2><ul>
<li>根据httpd版本，可能会有不同语法，根据情况修改配置文件，常见是<a href="https://httpd.apache.org/docs/2.4/zh-cn/upgrading.html" target="_blank" rel="external"><code>httpd2.2</code>与<code>httpd2.4</code>的区别</a><pre><code>Alias /zabbix /usr/share/zabbix
&lt;Directory &quot;/usr/share/zabbix&quot;&gt;
    Options FollowSymLinks
    AllowOverride None
    Allow from all
    &lt;IfModule mod_php5.c&gt;
        php_value max_execution_time 300
        php_value memory_limit 128M
        php_value post_max_size 16M
        php_value upload_max_filesize 2M
        php_value max_input_time 300
        php_value always_populate_raw_post_data -1
        php_value date.timezone PRC
     &lt;/IfModule&gt;
&lt;/Directory&gt;
</code></pre></li>
</ul>
<h2 id="配置数据库以及登录"><a href="#配置数据库以及登录" class="headerlink" title="配置数据库以及登录"></a>配置数据库以及登录</h2><ul>
<li>打开浏览器,访问<a href="http://hostname/zabbix/setup.php" target="_blank" rel="external">http://hostname/zabbix/setup.php</a>, 填写mysql相关信息,host填写为127.0.0.1以及检测软件是否满足要求</li>
<li>编辑/etc/zabbix/zabbix_server.conf文件设置mysql数据库信息</li>
<li>service zabbix-server start</li>
<li>登录，默认账号:Admin,密码:zabbix</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="优化以及配置"><a href="#优化以及配置" class="headerlink" title="优化以及配置"></a>优化以及配置</h2><ul>
<li>根据监控情况进行相关配置，如果监控主机数较多，需要配置<code>mysql</code>的<code>max-connections</code>选项</li>
<li>监控方式zabbix_agentd主动模式多的话,需要配置Trapper数量</li>
<li>监控方式zabbix_agentd被动方式多的话,需要配置Poller数量</li>
<li>当监控主机数量较多,建议使用主动模式或者proxy模式</li>
</ul>
]]></content>
      
